1
00:00:18,500 --> 00:00:21,490
♪Memories rise like towers so high♪

2
00:00:21,780 --> 00:00:24,760
♪Promises now seem ugly and dry♪

3
00:00:25,240 --> 00:00:28,180
♪Time devours like a wild beast♪

4
00:00:28,180 --> 00:00:31,090
♪It locks its gaze right onto me♪

5
00:00:32,120 --> 00:00:35,160
♪You're the one who knows how to let go♪

6
00:00:35,480 --> 00:00:38,630
♪You always leave, like the show♪

7
00:00:38,980 --> 00:00:41,500
♪I envy how you come and go♪

8
00:00:41,500 --> 00:00:44,440
♪For you, letting go is easy♪

9
00:00:45,580 --> 00:00:47,500
♪You tore right through my heart♪

10
00:00:47,500 --> 00:00:51,740
♪You turned away from my tears♪

11
00:00:52,180 --> 00:00:54,120
♪The story shatters into pieces♪

12
00:00:54,120 --> 00:00:56,920
♪All that's left is emptiness♪

13
00:00:57,150 --> 00:00:59,150
♪How am I supposed to carry on?♪

14
00:00:59,280 --> 00:01:01,190
♪You break the night like the dawn♪

15
00:01:01,190 --> 00:01:05,810
♪Leaving me lost in the deep♪

16
00:01:06,100 --> 00:01:09,250
♪Love is just an illusion♪

17
00:01:09,520 --> 00:01:12,400
♪Like a dream that I couldn't keep♪

18
00:01:13,340 --> 00:01:20,220
=Paramount=

19
00:01:20,300 --> 00:01:23,260
=Episode 2=

20
00:01:23,340 --> 00:01:24,940
(Paramount)

21
00:01:32,420 --> 00:01:33,270
Master Rong.

22
00:01:33,270 --> 00:01:39,580
(Master Rong, owner of Yongrong Casino)

23
00:01:50,550 --> 00:01:51,390
Master Rong.

24
00:01:52,030 --> 00:01:53,140
It's been so long.

25
00:01:53,550 --> 00:01:54,870
I've really missed you.

26
00:02:04,990 --> 00:02:05,900
Naughty.

27
00:02:07,180 --> 00:02:08,670
Share a drink with me first.

28
00:02:10,580 --> 00:02:12,860
(Five years ago, Bai family)

29
00:02:28,430 --> 00:02:29,270
Chairman Bai.

30
00:02:30,180 --> 00:02:31,540
Hand over the ledger, please.

31
00:02:32,220 --> 00:02:34,820
You actually dared to sell opium.

32
00:02:35,390 --> 00:02:36,230
If you keep this up,

33
00:02:36,430 --> 00:02:37,580
you'll drag me down as well.

34
00:02:37,750 --> 00:02:40,030
I won't give it to you.

35
00:02:41,820 --> 00:02:42,660
Keep going.

36
00:02:49,820 --> 00:02:51,460
Stop hitting him!

37
00:02:52,540 --> 00:02:53,540
Please, stop!

38
00:02:56,630 --> 00:02:57,750
Let go of my dad!

39
00:02:57,990 --> 00:02:58,830
Let him go!

40
00:02:59,580 --> 00:03:00,420
Dad.

41
00:03:06,540 --> 00:03:07,750
Please show us some mercy.

42
00:03:07,950 --> 00:03:09,350
Let us go, please.

43
00:03:10,100 --> 00:03:10,940
Luo.

44
00:03:12,100 --> 00:03:13,670
I'm begging you.

45
00:03:14,500 --> 00:03:17,220
I can't stand anyone dirtying my shoes.

46
00:03:18,780 --> 00:03:19,950
If things go bad for me,

47
00:03:20,630 --> 00:03:21,710
your whole family

48
00:03:22,310 --> 00:03:23,270
won't make it either.

49
00:03:23,390 --> 00:03:24,310
Stop!

50
00:03:24,500 --> 00:03:25,460
You troublemaker,

51
00:03:25,860 --> 00:03:26,860
got my shoes dirty.

52
00:03:27,990 --> 00:03:29,270
Don't hurt her anymore!

53
00:03:39,540 --> 00:03:40,510
Thank you all.

54
00:03:40,630 --> 00:03:41,820
Thanks for being here tonight.

55
00:03:43,150 --> 00:03:45,740
That's the end of Miss Bai's show.

56
00:03:45,820 --> 00:03:46,660
Thanks, everyone.

57
00:03:46,660 --> 00:03:47,510
Thank you.

58
00:03:49,150 --> 00:03:49,990
The new one?

59
00:03:53,270 --> 00:03:54,270
Go take a break first.

60
00:04:05,460 --> 00:04:06,300
Bai.

61
00:04:06,590 --> 00:04:07,900
What happened to you just now?

62
00:04:10,710 --> 00:04:11,820
Sorry, Aunt Mei.

63
00:04:12,540 --> 00:04:14,380
I wasn't feeling well just now.

64
00:04:15,100 --> 00:04:16,070
Any better?

65
00:04:16,460 --> 00:04:18,020
Let me have a moment alone.

66
00:04:18,740 --> 00:04:19,710
Alright.

67
00:04:34,630 --> 00:04:35,470
Master Rong.

68
00:04:35,820 --> 00:04:37,540
Does the new girl sing better,

69
00:04:37,540 --> 00:04:38,900
or am I still the best?

70
00:04:39,020 --> 00:04:39,990
You're the best.

71
00:05:12,020 --> 00:05:14,710
You two, go with Miss Shasha
for a late bite.

72
00:05:38,460 --> 00:05:39,340
Miss Bai.

73
00:05:43,150 --> 00:05:45,060
You sing well, that's for sure,

74
00:05:46,060 --> 00:05:47,470
and you handle your drinks too.

75
00:05:49,470 --> 00:05:50,540
You're our special guest.

76
00:05:50,940 --> 00:05:52,220
We want you to have a great time.

77
00:05:58,750 --> 00:05:59,590
Grab a seat there.

78
00:06:03,190 --> 00:06:05,060
Mr. Qian, I've been waiting for you.

79
00:06:05,540 --> 00:06:06,660
Having fun, Mr. Rong?

80
00:06:06,660 --> 00:06:07,540
Of course, I am.

81
00:06:08,190 --> 00:06:09,780
I see the Paramount is always packed now.

82
00:06:09,780 --> 00:06:11,190
Every seat's taken, it's thriving.

83
00:06:11,500 --> 00:06:12,990
Business just keeps getting better.

84
00:06:16,990 --> 00:06:18,430
I wonder if you

85
00:06:18,430 --> 00:06:19,940
have thought more about investing

86
00:06:20,500 --> 00:06:21,500
in my casino.

87
00:06:21,780 --> 00:06:23,220
Mr. Rong, you're a true veteran.

88
00:06:23,620 --> 00:06:24,750
I'm still gaining experience.

89
00:06:25,030 --> 00:06:26,390
How could I step in at your casino?

90
00:06:27,430 --> 00:06:28,750
Don't say that.

91
00:06:29,060 --> 00:06:30,310
You're a big name in Lin City.

92
00:06:30,310 --> 00:06:32,100
Everyone knows you.

93
00:06:34,140 --> 00:06:34,980
About the profits,

94
00:06:35,100 --> 00:06:35,940
you take 30%

95
00:06:36,060 --> 00:06:36,900
and I get 70%.

96
00:06:37,150 --> 00:06:37,990
All accounts

97
00:06:38,340 --> 00:06:39,940
are clear and transparent.

98
00:06:41,750 --> 00:06:42,590
Wait for my word.

99
00:06:47,940 --> 00:06:49,220
Let's have a proper talk

100
00:06:49,910 --> 00:06:51,030
at the banquet in three days.

101
00:06:51,270 --> 00:06:52,110
Alright.

102
00:06:57,540 --> 00:06:58,380
Mr. Qian.

103
00:06:58,990 --> 00:07:00,190
That's my glass.

104
00:07:01,910 --> 00:07:02,750
Sorry about that.

105
00:07:03,670 --> 00:07:04,510
I'll go get changed.

106
00:07:05,150 --> 00:07:06,060
Excuse me for a moment.

107
00:07:30,930 --> 00:07:31,870
Let me help you.

108
00:07:42,380 --> 00:07:43,820
What are you really after?

109
00:08:01,980 --> 00:08:04,100
Master Rong's banquet is in three days.

110
00:08:06,850 --> 00:08:08,500
I can go with you.

111
00:08:15,180 --> 00:08:16,260
I don't need a date.

112
00:08:28,860 --> 00:08:31,100
(Sincere Company Limited)

113
00:08:35,780 --> 00:08:36,900
(Kasili Lounge, Luo Shi)

114
00:08:38,540 --> 00:08:41,140
(Kasili)

115
00:08:51,790 --> 00:08:53,320
It's your turn next.

116
00:08:57,820 --> 00:09:04,420
(Luo Shi, Dockworkers Union Chairman)

117
00:09:06,940 --> 00:09:12,140
(Paramount)

118
00:09:14,110 --> 00:09:14,990
Hello, Mr. Luo.

119
00:09:14,990 --> 00:09:15,830
This way, please.

120
00:09:19,270 --> 00:09:21,040
♪It's hard to tell what's real♪

121
00:09:21,440 --> 00:09:24,040
♪I pick a rose♪

122
00:09:24,550 --> 00:09:26,790
♪And wear it close against my heart♪

123
00:09:27,080 --> 00:09:29,390
♪Come along with me♪

124
00:09:30,080 --> 00:09:31,600
♪As empty days drift by♪

125
00:09:31,600 --> 00:09:32,880
Mr. Luo,

126
00:09:33,270 --> 00:09:34,360
what brings you here today?

127
00:09:34,950 --> 00:09:36,040
Just running my business.

128
00:09:36,510 --> 00:09:37,480
All guests are welcome.

129
00:09:38,270 --> 00:09:39,990
♪Your first love♪

130
00:09:40,670 --> 00:09:42,670
♪Colder than the frost♪

131
00:09:43,160 --> 00:09:44,040
Am I not welcome?

132
00:09:44,040 --> 00:09:45,760
♪Why not come and sing with me?♪

133
00:09:46,040 --> 00:09:48,200
♪Let's lose ourselves in melody♪

134
00:09:49,230 --> 00:09:50,080
You are, of course.

135
00:09:52,940 --> 00:09:53,820
Mr. Luo's drinks

136
00:09:55,660 --> 00:09:56,500
are on me.

137
00:09:57,180 --> 00:09:58,020
Alright.

138
00:09:58,420 --> 00:09:59,820
Mr. Luo, after you.

139
00:09:59,820 --> 00:10:01,180
♪Your first love♪

140
00:10:01,380 --> 00:10:03,380
♪Colder than the frost♪

141
00:10:04,060 --> 00:10:04,980
♪Why not come♪

142
00:10:04,980 --> 00:10:05,980
Please wait a moment.

143
00:10:06,820 --> 00:10:09,340
♪Let's lose ourselves in melody♪

144
00:10:09,500 --> 00:10:11,980
♪Let's hold on tight♪

145
00:10:12,140 --> 00:10:15,540
♪To this sweet time♪

146
00:10:16,620 --> 00:10:20,020
Bravo.

147
00:10:23,450 --> 00:10:24,330
Today,

148
00:10:24,340 --> 00:10:25,940
I want to thank someone important.

149
00:10:45,540 --> 00:10:46,380
Mr. Luo,

150
00:10:48,060 --> 00:10:49,740
thanks for coming to support me.

151
00:11:02,620 --> 00:11:04,620
Time to give him something strong.

152
00:11:12,660 --> 00:11:13,580
Come here.

153
00:12:01,340 --> 00:12:02,260
It's so beautiful.

154
00:12:06,900 --> 00:12:07,820
Can you help me?

155
00:12:26,020 --> 00:12:27,260
Is this the "something strong"

156
00:12:27,780 --> 00:12:28,700
you meant?

157
00:12:29,420 --> 00:12:30,380
Stop talking.

158
00:12:31,020 --> 00:12:31,860
He's almost here.

159
00:12:32,760 --> 00:12:34,470
Miss Bai, you really know

160
00:12:35,820 --> 00:12:37,080
how to surprise people.

161
00:12:43,790 --> 00:12:46,650
Help me finish this scene properly.

162
00:13:47,120 --> 00:13:53,040
♪I can pretend like nothing's wrong♪

163
00:13:55,320 --> 00:13:59,920
♪You say you can't give me what I want♪

164
00:14:02,800 --> 00:14:05,680
♪But what did I ever ask for♪

165
00:14:06,320 --> 00:14:10,400
♪Just having you feels like a luxury♪

166
00:14:10,800 --> 00:14:14,160
♪The love you gave was never enough♪

167
00:14:14,640 --> 00:14:16,360
♪To keep me warm inside♪

168
00:14:18,720 --> 00:14:23,080
♪Should I be glad
I saw the cracks so soon?♪

169
00:14:23,200 --> 00:14:27,320
♪But how do I fix the hole in my soul?♪

170
00:14:27,720 --> 00:14:31,080
♪You found a thousand excuses♪

171
00:14:31,080 --> 00:14:34,160
♪Just to make me hurt more♪

172
00:14:35,200 --> 00:14:38,080
♪I reached out—
hoping you'd take my hand♪

173
00:14:38,080 --> 00:14:39,680
♪But you stepped back once again♪

174
00:14:39,840 --> 00:14:46,000
♪Back to where our first encounter began♪

175
00:14:46,240 --> 00:14:51,760
♪But you never walked toward me again♪

176
00:14:52,560 --> 00:14:56,920
♪I erased your name from my mind♪

177
00:14:56,920 --> 00:15:01,160
♪Lost my courage to reach for you♪

178
00:15:01,360 --> 00:15:05,240
♪I'm returning the loneliness we shared♪

179
00:15:05,240 --> 00:15:09,400
♪Still gasping from a hurt
too much to bear♪

180
00:15:09,640 --> 00:15:13,440
♪Your calm makes the whole room heavy♪

181
00:15:13,800 --> 00:15:17,440
♪There's not a hint of regret
in your eyes♪

182
00:15:17,800 --> 00:15:24,600
♪Maybe I never belonged in your life♪
